    {
        "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_524013",
        "quote": "'What is this', and 'How is this done?' are the first two questions to ask of any work of art. The second question immediately illuminates the first, but it often doesn't get asked. Perhaps it sounds too technical. Perhaps it sounds pedestrian.",
        "author": {
            "name": "James Fenton",
            "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_524013"
        },
        "topics": [
