                "name": "By The Time",
                "url": "/topics/by_the_time"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_523972",
        "quote": "When we study Shakespeare on the page, for academic purposes, we may require all kinds of help. Generally, we read him in modern spelling and with modern punctuation, and with notes. But any poetry that is performed - from song lyric to tragic speech - must make its point, as it were, without reference back.",
        "author": {
            "name": "James Fenton",
            "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_523972"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Back",
                "url": "/topics/back"
            },
            {
                "name": "Notes",
                "url": "/topics/notes"
            },
            {
                "name": "Study",
                "url": "/topics/study"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_523973",
        "quote": "Poetry carries its history within it, and it is oral in origin. Its transmission was oral. Its transmission today is still in part oral, because we become acquainted with poetry through nursery rhymes, which we hear before we can read.",
        "author": {
            "name": "James Fenton",
            "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_523973"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Through",
                "url": "/topics/through"
            },
            {
                "name": "Which",
                "url": "/topics/which"
            },
            {
                "name": "Still",
                "url": "/topics/still"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_523975",
        "quote": "Working alone on a poem, a poet is of all artists the most free. The poem can be written with a modicum of technology, and can be published, in most cases, quite cheaply.",
        "author": {
            "name": "James Fenton",
            "url": "/quotes/james_fenton_523975"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Technology",
